{"tid":1504550,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有冇機會，香港暴力示威，係中共自編自導自演","createTime":"2019-08-25T10:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T11:41:52.000Z","uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c0f3a2427b4ad14a9850c63d7b1fadb21ec08e68","tid":1504550,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:50:19.000Z","msg":"因為香港反送中激嬲左共產黨。<br />\n所以要形做香港暴力示威的形象和氣氛俾世界睇？<br />\n<br />\n要證實呢點好簡單，就係大家等到十月一日<br />\n中共講明十月一日前要止暴制亂。<br />\n理論上，如果係市民自發，十月一日先最亂。<br />\n但如果係中共和警方搞出來的一場戲，十月一日反而會好平靜，官員齊齊放煙花慶祝。<br />\n <br />\n真相係點，大家拭目以待 。"},{"pid":"3852cdd35935129785ebb9d847e20e853f753c63","tid":1504550,"uid":151578,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:51:19.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"d707b6870f32b09548111a6db19cd20bfea739df","tid":1504550,"uid":3682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:51:58.000Z","msg":"blocked"},{"pid":"5a2a123cd4dad3e469ddfbd56f8e91fbead76241","tid":1504550,"uid":239453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:52:20.000Z","msg":"on撚9"},{"pid":"c6159060bbfde4e62562c354fc063061881df430","tid":1504550,"uid":160166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:52:31.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"89f148ad84b87f650bf11299efa2001f9aa4bbe8","tid":1504550,"uid":149662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:52:54.000Z","msg":"block"},{"pid":"b08c19080843d9effabe0f717469b0be01d9962b","tid":1504550,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:52:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"43bd6be972be7fa013c4946091214d28b61cbeae","tid":1504550,"uid":138092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:53:03.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"ea712b6e528bf71c40ff34efd30d827e02f66a2b","tid":1504550,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T10:54:17.000Z","msg":"BLOCKED"},{"pid":"0cbafa7ab08ed069b